	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have about 5k to twink a monk with, and I was wondering what I should get him.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am thinking about either 2FBs and an FBSS or a peacebringer.  Any suggestions would be helpful.  THanks<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
