	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually, from what Ive seen so far in some of my own, non-scientific trials, the additional hitpoints you receive from STA items works similarly to the way INT and WIS items works for INT and WIS casters.<br><br>So, I dont believe that you get a bonus to your base stats, but you do get a bonus based on AC/level.&nbsp;&nbsp;Hope that is correct and makes sense.<br><br>Lunar<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
