onsistently made this game harder and harder.. twinkin and PLing are almost necesary in my mind to get out of the boring and hard to group levels of 1-20..<br><br>I would also like to take this time to say I think it sucks Verant does nerf the game.. Fear kitin by necs is a good example of where verant forces a class to play a certain way through nerfs.. because necs can kick ass with fear kiting they have been nerfed so much that they can't kill anything any other way... (gettin off soap box now)<br><br>Hope this helps a little.. good luck when you do start your monk.<br><br>-Pulrial Phazt<br>45 Monk, Brell<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
